As of July 7th, 2024 all of these ideas have been scrapped and the entire game has
been rebuilt to be in line with Dungeons and Dragons; While the campaign setting is
original to avoid copyright issues, the basics are kept in line with items released
under the Open Gaming License.

Races: Dragonborn, Drow, Dwarf, Elf, Half-Elf, Halfling, Half-Orc, Human, Gnome and
Tiefling.

Classes: Cleric, Druid, Fighter, Mage, Rogue
Classes still to be added: Barbarian, Bard, Monk, Paladin, Ranger, Sorcerer

